Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:30.71,Main,Shizue,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy! What about the bomb shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:32.40,Main,Shizue,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:00.88,sign_1407_3_Tokyo__Present_D,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Tokyo: Present Day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:07.10,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is peaceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:13.95,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,I live a totally normal, uneventful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:18.39,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,I graduated from college, got a job \Nat a major general contracting firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:21.85,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,worked my way up the ladder, \Nand started making decent money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:24.24,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a perfectly content 37-year-old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:30.16,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything missing in my \Nlife right now, it's a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:34.16,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I haven't had a \Ngirlfriend in all my 37 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:38.55,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,But not having one doesn't \Nbother me at all, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:41.00,Main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.87,Main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.54,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Tamura, sorry I'm a bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:49.44,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,So, what'd you want to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:52.37,Main,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! I'm Sawatari Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.77,Main,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,I see you around a lot, but this \Nis our first time speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:59.42,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Hi. I'm Mikami Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:01.69,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,I know who you are, of course. You're famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:03.48,Main,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Famous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:06.24,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I mean, all those rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:09.03,Main,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What rumors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.93,Main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, Miho. He's just teasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:14.33,Main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,Go easy on her, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:15.89,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:19.83,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, anyway? \NIs he looking for marriage advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:23.14,Main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,No need to stand around. \NLet's talk while we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.20,Main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,You like yakiniku, don't you, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.25,Main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,I booked a great place for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.83,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, he arranged one of \Nmy favorites for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.47,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Kid sure knows how to treat his senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:34.05,Main,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,It's just up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:37.73,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I should offer \Nthem my congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:46.82,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Tamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:07.06,Main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.55,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:13.91,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,It's too hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.76,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't... want this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:18.97,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:22.80,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Heat Resistance acquisition successful.
