Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.38,Main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.60,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:49.65,Main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,All I really wanted to do...\Nwas show off Sawatari to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.48,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.06,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.46,Main,Miho,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:00.78,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.91,Main,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,And take care of my computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:10.08,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd die a virgin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:13.25,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm reborn, I'll be a lot more aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.27,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll screw every girl I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:20.18,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Unique skill: Predator \Nacquisition successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:18.18,sign_7648_110_Unique_Skill_Pre,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(731,1)}Unique Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:18.97,sign_7648_110_Unique_Skill_Pre,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Unique Skill\N{\fs24}Predator
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.18,sign_7648_110_Unique_Skill_Pre,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Unique Skill\N{\fs24}Predator\N{\fs18}Acquired
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.85,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,If a guy who's still a \Nvirgin at 30 is a magician,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:29.43,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,then, given how close I was\Nto 40, I would've been a sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:32.58,Italics,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,I could've even made it \Nto the rank of great sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:35.86,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Extra skill: Sage acquisition successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:33.94,sign_7648_110_Unique_Skill_Pre,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H272419&\fad(396,1)}Extra Skill
